summary: Ranging from live action to voice-overs, Kobi is already building up an incredible resume. Despite this, he can’t pick a...
caption:
Ranging from live action to voice-overs, Kobi is already building up an incredible resume. Despite this, he can’t pick a favorite project.

“I’ve worked on indie projects, some independent films, several cartoons, and of course, ‘The Punisher’, but at this point in my career, I can’t pick just one favorite,” he reveals. “I feel lucky to have worked on so many different types of projects.”

For the young actor, his passion for acting pushes him to do more. With several projects in the works at the moment, he can’t say anything just yet about them. Kobi does, however, have advice for other kids who want to become an actor.

“Go for it,” he states, simply. “Follow your dreams. But just know, it’s a job – it’s hard work. If you love it, it’s worth it!”

#KobiFrumer #ThePunisher #Netflix #Marvel #ZachLieberman #Throwback

summary: So I wanted to post something #spidermanintothespiderverse related because I just saw it and loved it, but haven’t had time to...
caption:
So I wanted to post something #spidermanintothespiderverse related because I just saw it and loved it, but haven’t had time to draw something new. So here is an old drawing I did during the summer that I never got around to finishing until now (hey it’s still Spider-Man, right!).

This is a panel from an @nba themed super hero comic I was drawing in my spare time called #superteam. I wanted it to be like a superhero/nba comedy, mash up, parody thing. Taking all the drama of the nba season and make little comedy strips of them. I still might do it!

This is Utah Jazz guard Donovan Mitchell as Spider-Man, his nickname is Spida so that’s the level of jokes we’re dealing with here….

#basketball #comics #marvel #youlikejazz #donovanmitchell

summary: Then Again by wordsinwinters is very good!
question: Then Again by wordsinwinters is very good!
answer:
First shout out goes to @wordsinwinters’s series Then Again, a Peter Parker x Reader slow-burn that starts with bed-sharing, one of the greatest tropes in fan fiction history for the immediate conflict it brings. 

This story dives deep into character and the extended universe around Peter, and has e a wonderful sense of pacing. The story is currently on hiatus but there are over 20 binge-able chapters currently available.

Go check out and support this wonderful spider-man story!

Thanks for the recommend, @stitchbeatle!
